    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fs-4" href="/">SAJAG</a>
            <div>
                <a href="/learn" class="nav-link active text-white d-inline-block me-3">Learn</a>
                <a href="/api/auth/login" class="btn btn-outline-light">Login</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h1>Learn & Prepare</h1>
            <p class="lead">Knowledge is the key to resilience. Here are some basic preparedness measures for common disasters.</p>
        </div>

        <hr class="my-5">

        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>Earthquake Safety</h2>
                <p>India has a history of devastating earthquakes. Knowing what to do is critical.</p>
                <ul class="list-group">
                    <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-success"><strong>DO:</strong> Drop, Cover, and Hold On.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-success"><strong>DO:</strong> If outside, stay outside and move away from buildings.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-danger"><strong>DON'T:</strong> Use elevators during an earthquake.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-danger"><strong>DON'T:</strong> Stand in doorways.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="ratio ratio-16x9">
                    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/G3hfugI1oXQ" title="Earthquake Safety" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="my-5">

        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>Flood Safety</h2>
                <p>Floods are one of the most common natural disasters in India. Follow these guidelines to stay safe.</p>
                 <ul class="list-group">
                    <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-success"><strong>DO:</strong> Move to higher ground immediately.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-success"><strong>DO:</strong> Listen to emergency broadcasts for updates.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-danger"><strong>DON'T:</strong> Walk or drive through floodwaters.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-danger"><strong>DON'T:</strong> Touch electrical equipment if you are wet or standing in water.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                 <div class="ratio ratio-16x9 bg-secondary text-white d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                    [Flood Safety Video]
                 </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>